Isadore Plotke v. The Estate of E. L. Negley et al.Appeal from the County Court of Cook County.Opinion filed February 14, 1899.W. A. Marsh, solicitor for appellant; G. W. Ambrose, of counsel.Rosenthal, Kjjrz & Hirschl, attorneys for appellees.

Bill of exceptions does not purport to contain all the testimony. The certificate of the clerk of the trial court does not purport to give a transcript of the record upon that branch of the case involved in this appeal. Affirmed.
